These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, musician, pilot
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, game, vegafina, ritmeester
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, daisy, aconite
 1. the vegafina-smoker is in an odd position##4
 2. the pilot is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 3. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the pilot##6
 5. the musician is somewhere to the right of the electrician##5
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the firefighter##8
 8. the firefighter is not the person who growsaconite##6
 9. the electrician is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
10. the person who growsamaryllis is the ritmeester-smoker##1
11. the firefighter is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
12. the firefighter is in an even position##4
13. the pilot is not to the right of the person who growsaconite##8
14. the vegafina-smoker is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job    | electrician         | pilot     | musician     | firefighter         |
| Cigar   | game | ritmeester    | vegafina     | havana |
| Flower   | balloon-flower       | amaryllis | aconite | daisy       |

