.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, french, nigerian, dutch
House: craftsman, ranch-style, gothic-revival, colonial
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, tulip, aconite
 1. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the colonial house##8
 2. the nigerian is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the dutch is the ranch-style house##1
 5. the craftsman house is not the nigerian##6
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the dutch is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 8. the indonesian is on the left of the dutch##1
 9. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
10. the indonesian is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | nigerian          | indonesian      | dutch      | french   |
| House        | gothic-revival     | craftsman | ranch-style | colonial      |
| Flower      | aconite | zinnia    | poppy  | tulip |

