.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, fisherman, pilot, architect
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, dutch, brazilian, indonesian
4 different games are played: chess, backgammon, billiard, bridge
 1. the chef is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 3. the chef is on the right of the indonesian##1
 4. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 5. the person playing chess is not the mexican##6
 6. the mexican is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the mexican is not to the right of the indonesian##8
 8. the architect is on the left of the brazilian##1
 9. the fisherman is in an even position##4
10. the architect is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Job         | pilot  | fisherman | architect | chef |
| Nationality   | dutch  | mexican      | indonesian | brazilian        |
| Game     | chess | billiard       | bridge    | backgammon     |

