.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, writer, teacher, scientist
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, 7up, almond-milk
4 different games are played: go, poker, mah-jongg, whist
 1. the writer is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the freelancer##5
 4. the freelancer is on the far left##1
 5. the writer is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the scientist##8
 7. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 8. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
 9. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
10. the scientist is the person playing mah-jongg##1
11. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Job   | freelancer   | scientist | writer    | teacher |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola     | sprite   | almond-milk     |
| Game   | go | mah-jongg   | poker | whist    |

