.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, cat, chinchilla
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, begonia, rose
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, papaya, plum, blueberry
 1. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
 5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person who growsrose is not the owner of the cat##6
 7. the owner of the bird is not the person eating plum##6
 8. the person who growsazalea is the person eating plum##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
10. the person eating blueberry is the owner of the cat##1
11. the person eating blueberry is not to the left of the person who growsbegonia##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | cat       | bird | fish  | chinchilla    |
| Flower   | begonia       | rose    | azalea | iris    |
| Food         | blueberry | pomegranate   | plum   | papaya |

