.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, bird, hamster, horse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, april, march
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, lacrosse, rugby
 1. the owner of the hamster is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the person who's birthday is in march##7
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is between the owner of the cat and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
10. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
11. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Pet          | bird      | hamster      | horse | cat |
| Birthday   | april | october    | march | may     |
| Sport   | climbing    | lacrosse | rugby  | swimming |

