The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, tulip, lily
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, july, january, november
 1. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is not the person eating lettuce##6
 3. the person who growssunflower is between the person who growstulip and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person who growslily##6
 8. the person eating strawberry is not to the right of the person who growslily##8
 9. the person who growslily is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8
10. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
11. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
12. the person eating lettuce is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
13. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
