The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, parkour, soccer, climbing
1. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
2. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the person traveling to miami and the person traveling to liverpool##7
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
4. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
5. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
6. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
7. the person traveling to miami is the person who's sport is parkour##1
8. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the person driving the airplane##7
9. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Transport      | airplane     | bike | van  | roller |
| City          | new-york | miami   | boston | liverpool |
| Sport   | snowboarding     | parkour   | climbing      | soccer      |

