The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, august, july
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, swisher, cain, aristoff
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the prince-smoker##1
2. the person playing poker is not to the right of the swisher-smoker##8
3. the aristoff-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in july##2
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person playing poker is not the cain-smoker##6
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the cain-smoker is somewhere between the aristoff-smoker and the swisher-smoker##7
8. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
9. the cain-smoker is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | poker | scrabble     | mah-jongg  | go |
| Birthday           | april      | july        | august   | february |
| Cigar         | swisher  | cain | aristoff | prince       |

 